{"tid":690666,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳林燕妮肺癌離世 享年75歲","createTime":"2018-06-05T05:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T18:48:20.000Z","uid":130626,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"af642870d0bdf1cd0d32de09c5d868b381440221","tid":690666,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:10:09.000Z","msg":"今日有報道指「香江才女」林燕妮日前因肺癌於養和醫院離世，享年七十五歲，近年身體衰弱，臥牀休養，她於2016年患肺癌，曾接受化療及電療，可惜仍不敵癌魔。<br />\n<br />\n林燕妮曾與李小龍兄長李忠琛結婚，二人育有一子，早前與著名填詞人黃霑相戀12年，後因第三者介入，結束多年情；林燕妮為家中長女，有兩弟一妹，林燕妮為填詞人林振強胞姐，妹妹林雁妮早於1981年因淋巴癌離世，林振強和林振剛亦淋巴癌於2003年離世。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/05/130942_8828ef02bf7e3222b52c58df393dd882.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F05%2F130942_8828ef02bf7e3222b52c58df393dd882.png&h=29911873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180605/58279725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180605%2F58279725&d=lY5kZ2wbYh2qA7mbLejyKoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=98057be9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180605%2F58279725&h=da79dc22\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180605/58279725</a>"},{"pid":"a49b64142326f338f428321f0bfdb3411632add7","tid":690666,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7f9de46d1b305a8a023118233d19f907074363","tid":690666,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:19:49.000Z","msg":"一陣遍地黃金, 人才輩出即年代<br />\n一路好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f540cb3669cb89810872